snippet.title: I'm counting to 6...  -  Teaser
snippet.description:
Friends! I haven't released new projects for a whole year. All this time, I've been helping my friends develop their games, acting as a consultant. I also helped in the development of a short film for the game "September 7th". But for the last month I have been working on a new project "I'm counting to 6..." and it is almost ready. 

Steam page👇👇
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2717260/___6/
